			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I like the idea and have sent a couple feedback in-game suggesting it.  Forgive me for not reading the entire thread, but I'm going to tackle some issues that I can easily foresee.
<br />

<br />
To address the issue of "loot for pets and guild relations", that is entirely up to the guilds to handle.  If they want to allow meges to spend DKP on pet loot, that's their business and no one else's.  Personally, I don't think guilds would allow it.  I think they would let loot that would otherwise rot or be shuffled to the 3rd string of twinks go to pets instead.
<br />

<br />
To address using pets as an extra bank, how's this:  Once you drop an item into a pet slot it is there forever, until replaced by another item.  The replaced item is destroyed.  Items cannot be removed from pets.
<br />

<br />
If you want to limit it to droppables only, I don't have major issues with that.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
